title: Murphy, Mets send Cubs to brink of elimination with 5-2 win
text: Murphy, Mets send Cubs to brink of elimination with 5-2 win Oct. 20, 2015 Updated 8:20 p.m. 1 of 21 The Mets' Daniel Murphy scores past Cubs catcher Miguel Montero during the seventh inning of Game 3. Murphy scored from third on a ball hit by Lucas Duda. DAVID J. PHILLIP, THE ASSOCIATED PRESS 1 of 21 The Mets' David Wright hits a double during the seventh inning of Game 3 against the Cubs.
